Thanks for reporting. This is a bug in the emulator, we are working on a fix.
The string &quot;b~&lt;app_id&gt;&quot; is the full app id in the cloud datastore. You should be able to get consistent data by appending this &quot;b~&quot; in the import request:

    curl -X POST localhost:&lt;emulator_port&gt;/v1/projects/b~&lt;app-id&gt;:import -H &#39;Content-Type: application/json&#39; -d &#39;{&quot;input_url&quot;:&quot;&lt;local_folder&gt;/&lt;file&gt;.overall_export_metadata&quot;}&#39;
